Now that the sun is returning to us residents of the northern hemisphere, have any of you received a seed catalog yet?
 
 I got on the mailing lists of all the major seed companies so that my mailbox would overflow with their catalogs, bringing me pictures of plush, Edenic gardens in which I vicariously live while awaiting winter to slowly begin losing its grip. I expect to begin seeing them within 2-3 weeks.
 
 Let me know if and when you receive one. It's much like spotting the first robin of spring.
I haven't had a seed catalogue yet, but I have received a junk mail advertising food hampers for Christmas 2006 !
